verbose_text: Additionally, the combination of melatonin and sorafenib resulted in the greatest decreased in cell proliferation index (Ki67 positive) and enhanced more cell apoptosis as determined by cleaved PARP and TUNEL staining compared with melatonin or sorafenib alone.
evidence: melatonin and sorafenib resulted in the greatest decreased in cell proliferation index (Ki67-positive) and enhanced more cell apoptosis
